 Participate in software planning and testing 
 Update tracking operations planning documents 
 Monitor files transfer from stadium to production centers 
 Support on operations travel logistics 
 
 DO YOU HAVE THESE ESSENTIALS? 
 Several years of experience with tracking system SportVU 
 Experienced in operational and technical testing of tracking systems 
 Working hours flexibility 
 High knowledge in football rules 
 Technical skills 
 
